{"tid":2267201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"WHO秘書長譚德塞自主隔離 曾接觸武漢肺炎確診者","createTime":"2020-11-02T01:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T12:07:37.000Z","uid":337052,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"8c6c117fafd6e83a2a2b8d98ba6f2bd4a8475ddb","tid":2267201,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T01:59:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">WHO秘書長譚德塞自主隔離 曾接觸武漢肺炎確診者</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2020/11/02 08:57<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgcdn.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20201102/2000x1500_0822623976733.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgcdn.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20201102%2F2000x1500_0822623976733.jpg&h=b536fae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚德塞（圖）1日表示，他經證實有接觸到武漢肺炎篩檢呈陽性反應者，接下來幾天會自主隔離並在家工作。（<a href=\"http://圖取自twitter.com/DrTedros\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%9C%96%E5%8F%96%E8%87%AAtwitter.com%2FDrTedros&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxQbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=4ba1631e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">圖取自twitter.com/DrTedros</a>）<br />\n<br />\n（中央社日內瓦1日綜合外電報導）<span class=\"red\">世界衛生組織（WHO）秘書長譚德塞今天表示，他經證實有接觸到2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19，武漢肺炎）篩檢呈陽性反應者</span>，但他也說自己現在感覺良好，沒有任何症狀。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）在推文中說：「我經證實有接觸到2019冠狀病毒疾病篩檢呈陽性反應的人。我現在感覺很好，沒有出現任何症狀，但接下來幾天我會自行隔離，遵守WHO規定，並在家工作。」（譯者：李晉緯/核稿：盧映孜）1091102<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/DrTedros/status/1323032927492542465?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrTedros%2Fstatus%2F1323032927492542465%3Fs%3D20&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxQbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=a0151706\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrTedros%2Fstatus%2F1323032927492542465%3Fs%3D20&h=edbad66c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/DrTedros/status/1323032927492542465?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202011020010.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202011020010.aspx&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxQbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=0ca5ff30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202011020010.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"40523e9debc627aa886a4a1c0c6e00b63246eda6","tid":2267201,"uid":337052,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ElxjQgLWMAEFErv?format=png&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FElxjQgLWMAEFErv%3Fformat%3Dpng%26name%3Dsmall&h=84f9316a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"247d19e97e2d22bc9d985ac6e9ea60e93ba8b0d6","tid":2267201,"uid":302236,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:01:14.000Z","msg":"原來佢重未死"},{"pid":"c74392ebaa1474bb19d8c987a66bb762c40120e6","tid":2267201,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f02783a2125ca011a7e036a9bff717c9b6f9e5d","tid":2267201,"uid":39200,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:02:05.000Z","msg":"佢就好啦, 咁快可以幫雜總試藥"},{"pid":"17de73dadda1d328a9ae9350c55aba5246ad8320","tid":2267201,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:02:39.000Z","msg":"希望直接落地獄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f4ebbd8f2d3ab86fe1172d79c9b63bc3dd75c6","tid":2267201,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T02:03:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/04/05/2488961-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F04%2F05%2F2488961-PH.jpg&h=16eac3c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"978b2734ca